    "description": "This has all the classic elements of a caesar salad but in the form of a luxurious sandwich. What's not to love? You'll sandwich juicy marinated chicken with crispy bacon and a knock-out caesar dressing. Serve with rosemary fries and cheesy lettuce wedges and you're sorted!",
